    "Inscribed Angle = Half Central Angle": "内接角 = 圆心角的一半",
    "Tangent-Radius Theorem": "切线-半径定理",
    "Tangent is perpendicular to radius at point of tangency": "切线在切点处垂直于半径",
    "Two tangents from external point are congruent": "从外部点的两条切线是全等的",
    "Area of a Circle": "圆的面积",
    "Area = πr²": "面积 = πr²",
    "Sector": "扇形",
