    "Sector Area = θ/360° × πr²": "扇形面积 = θ/360° × πr²",
    "Segment": "线段",
    "Area of Segment": "弓形面积",
    "Intersecting Chords Theorem": "相交弦定理",
    "If two chords intersect, then the product of segments of one chord equals the product of segments of the other chord": "如果两条弦相交，则一条弦的线段乘积等于另一条弦的线段乘积",
    "Secant-Secant Theorem": "割线-割线定理",
