    "Super-heavy Elements": "超重元素",
    ": Elements with very high atomic numbers (e.g., oganesson, element 118); extremely unstable.": "：原子序数非常高的元素（例如oganesson，118号元素）；极不稳定。",
    "Electromagnetic Spectrum": "电磁波谱",
    ": The full range of electromagnetic radiation from radio waves to gamma rays.": "：从无线电波到伽马射线的全范围电磁辐射。",
    "Wavelength (╬╗)": "波长 (λ)",
