    "Speed of Light": "光速",
    ": c = ╬╗ ├ù ╬╜ = 3.0 ├ù 10Γü╕ m/s; wavelength and frequency are inversely related.": "：c = λ × ν = 3.0 × 10⁸ m/s；波长和频率成反比。",
    "Atomic Emission Spectrum": "原子发射光谱",
