    "Latin-Based Symbols": "拉丁语符号",
    ": Some symbols come from Latin names (Na = natrium/sodium, Fe = ferrum/iron, Au = aurum/gold).": "：一些符号来自拉丁名称（Na = natrium/钠，Fe = ferrum/铁，Au = aurum/金）。",
    "Element vs. Compound": "元素与化合物",
    ": Elements have single symbols; compounds combine symbols (e.g., HΓééO, NaCl).": "：元素有单个符号；化合物结合符号（例如 H₂O, NaCl）。",
    "s Orbital Shape": "s 轨道形状",
    ": Spherical; exists in every energy level.": "：球形；存在于每个能级。",
    "p Orbital Shape": "p 轨道形状",
    ": Dumbbell (figure-eight); 3 orientations along x, y, z axes.": "：哑铃形（8字形）；沿 x, y, z 轴的 3 个方向。",
    "d Orbital Shape": "d 轨道形状",
    ": Clover-leaf (most) and donut-dumbbell; 5 orientations.": "：三叶草形（大多数）和甜甜圈-哑铃形；5 个方向。",
    "f Orbital Shape": "f 轨道形状",
    ": Complex multi-lobed shapes; 7 orientations.": "：复杂的多瓣形状；7 个方向。",
    "Orbital Size": "轨道大小",
