    ": A region where the probability of finding an electron is zero.": "：发现电子概率为零的区域。",
    "Reactivity Trends": "反应性趋势",
    ": Metals become more reactive going down a group; nonmetals become more reactive going up.": "：金属沿族向下反应性增强；非金属沿族向上反应性增强。",
    "Effective Nuclear Charge (Zeff)": "有效核电荷 (Zeff)",
    ": The net positive charge felt by valence electrons after shielding: Zeff = Z ΓêÆ S.": "：屏蔽后价电子感受到的净正电荷：Zeff = Z − S。",
    "More Shielding": "更多屏蔽",
    ": As you go DOWN a group, more inner electron shells increase shielding, so outer electrons are held less tightly.": "：当你沿族向下时，更多的内电子层增加屏蔽，因此外层电子被束缚得不那么紧。",
