    "A statement (or proposition) is a sentence that is either true (T) or false (F), but not both.": "语句（或命题）是一个要么为真（T）要么为假（F）的句子，但不能两者兼有。",
    "Alternate interior angles: On opposite sides of the transversal, between the lines. ∠3 and ∠6.": "内错角：在截线的两侧，在两条线之间。∠3和∠6。",
