    "Assume the opposite: Assume that the conclusion you want to prove is false (negate the conclusion).": "假设相反：假设你要证明的结论是假的（否定结论）。",
    "Two figures are similar if and only if one can be mapped to the other by a similarity transformation.": "两个图形相似当且仅当一个可以通过相似变换映射到另一个。",
