    "Use logical reasoning: Use definitions, theorems, and given information to reason from the assumption.": "使用逻辑推理：使用定义、定理和已知信息从假设进行推理。",
    "A square is a parallelogram that is both a rectangle and a rhombus. It has all the properties of both:": "正方形是既是矩形又是菱形的平行四边形。它具有两者的所有性质：",
