    "A dilation centered at Point O with scale factor k maps every Point P to a Point P' such that OP' = k × OP.": "以点O为中心、比例因子为k的位似变换将每个点P映射到点P'，使得 OP' = k × OP。",
    "Use when you know: AAS, ASA, or SSA (two angles and a side, or two sides and an Angle opposite one of them).": "当你知道：AAS、ASA或SSA（两个角和一条边，或两条边和其中一条的对角）时使用。",
